    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E92 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This specimen features individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, delivering linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, feeding power through a GKN-Viscodrive limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the rod bearings have been proactively replaced with treated shells and ARP hardware. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the signature carbon fiber roof for optimal mass distribution. The exterior finish and Novillo leather interior are in pristine, showroom state, free of typical bolster wear or cosmetic imperfections. This is a mechanically sorted, collector-grade vehicle for the enthusiast who demands peak performance and structural integrity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
